          "id": "Markdown-29a36d81-b709-45e0-88da-19065409618b",
          "text": "Functionality that falls outside of the [roadmap](/proposals/puck-platform-recipe/roadmap) can be supported by Measured Professional Services.\n\nExamples of relevant services Measured can offer:\n\n- Themeable component libraries\n- Puck editor configuration\n- Deep integration into an existing stack or content system\n- Custom dashboard interfaces\n- Custom Puck plugins\n- Advice, consultancy and architecture\n\n## Fees\n\nMeasured Professional Services are charged at a rate of $195/hour on a time-and-materials basis. The minimum billable block is 4 hours.\n\nRetainers available on request.",
